.name
ACalc
.description
A small calculator with floating point, hexadecimal and
decimal modes.  Has 10 memories, saves the last result in
the clipboard, may be used with the mouse or keyboard.
With OS 2.x and 3.0, may be installed as a Commodity.
Includes both French and English versions.  
.short
Small calculator with FP, hex and dec.
.type
Programmer's Tool
.exectype
Binary only.
.author  
Denis Gounelle
.described-by
David Zaroski (cz253@cleveland.freenet.edu)
